: null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013477, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon Muhammad, the seal of Prophets. Peace be on Ali, the Commander of the faithful. Peace be upon Fatima Zahra, the chief of the women of the worlds. Peace be upon Khadija al-Kubra, the mother of the believers. Peace be upon Hasan and Husain, the chiefs of all the youth of Paradise together.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAA MOHAMMADIN KHAATE-MIN NABIY-YEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA A’LIYYIN AMEERIL MO-MENEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA FAATEMA-TAZ ZAHRAA-E SAYYADA-TE NESAA-AL AA’LAMEE-NA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA KHADEE-JATAL KUBRAA UMMIL MO-MENEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAL HASANE WAL HUSAINE SAYYA-DAIY SHA-BAABE AHLIL JANNA-TE MINAL KHALQE AJMA-EE’NA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ خَاتِمِ النَّبِیِّیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی عَلِیٍّ اَمِیْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی فَاطِمَۃَ الزَّهْرَائِ سَیِّدَۃِ نِسَائَ الْعَالَمِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی خَدِیْجَۃَ الْكُبْرٰی اُمِّ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْحَسَنِ وَالْحُسَیْنِ سَیِّدَیْ شَبَابِ اَهْلِ الْجَنَّۃِ مِنَ الْخَلْقِ اَجْمَعِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013478, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon the rest of the Imams of the Muslims; Ali, Muhammad, Jaffar, Musa, Ali, Muhammad, Ali, Hasan and the successor, the guide, the guided, the fulfiller of the promise to the believers. Peace be upon the proximate angels and the righteous servants. Peace be upon the righteous servant, the sincere friend and the God fearing scholar, buried in the land of Ghari, Kumail bin Ziyaad.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAA SAA-E-RE A-EMA-TIL MUSLE-MEENA A’LIYYIN WA MOHAMMADIN WA JA’FARIN WA MOOSAA WA A’LIYYIN WA MOHAMMADIN WA A’LIYYIN WAL HASANE WAL KHALA-FIL HAADIL MAHDIY-YE MUNJE-ZE WA’DIL MO-MENEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA MALAA-E-KATE-HIL MOQARRA-BEENA WA E’BAADE-HIS SAALE-HEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAL A’BDIS SAALE-HIL WALIYYIN NAASE-HIL AA’LE-MIT TAQIYYIL MADFOO-NE BE-ARZIL GHARIYYE KOMAIY-LIBNE ZIYAADIN.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی سَائِرِ اَئِمَۃِ الْمُسْلِمِیْنَ عَلِیٍّ وَ مُحَمَّدٍ وَ جَعْفَرٍ وَ مُوْسٰی وَ عَلِیٍّ وَ مُحَمَّدٍ وَ عَلِیٍّ وَ الْحَسَنِ وَ الْخَلَفِ الْهَادِی الْمَهْدِیِّ مُنْجِزِ وَ عْدِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مَلَائِكَتِهِ الْمُقَرَبِیْنَ وَ عِبَادِهِ الصَّالِحِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْعَبْدِ الصَّالِحِ، الْوَلِیِّ النَّاصِحِ الْعَالِمِ التَّقِیِّ الْمَدْفُوْنِ بِاَرْضِ الْغَرِیِّ كُمَیْلِ بْنِ زِیَادٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013479, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon the one who was perfected by him ie. Imam Ali (a.s), who himself was perfect in attributes and the commander of the Prophet in the wars, who entrusted him the secret and taught him Dua’e Khizr (Dua’e Kumail), who informed him about the soul and the reality, then through it he became enlightened. I testify that you have contributed to the truth, you oriented to the path of truth and guidance and kept away from falsehood and obstinacy.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAA MAN AK-MALA-HUL KAA-MELE FIS SE-FAATE WAL AMEERE FIL GHAZA-WAATE WA WADDA-A’HUS SIRRA WA A’LLAMA-HO DO-AA’-AL KHIZRE WA AKHBARA-HO A’NIN NAFSE WAL HAQEE-QATE FA-SAARA FEE-HAAZAA BASEE-RATEEN. ASH-HADO ANNA-KA QAD ADDAIY-TA ILAL HAQQE, WA WAJJAH-TA MINHAA-JAS SADQE WAR-RASHAA-DE WA A’RAZ-TA A’NIL BAA-TELE WAL E’NAADE.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مَنْ اَكْمَلَهُ الْكَامِلِ فِیْ الصِّفَاتِ وَالْاَمِیْرِ فِیْ الْغَزَوَاتِ وَ وَدَّعَهُ السِّرَّ وَ عَلَّمَهُ دُعَائَ الْخِضْرِ وَ اَخْبَرَهُ عَنِ النَّفْسِ وَالْحَقِیْقَ