BlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013480, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon one of the disciples of the strong rope of Allah (Imam Ali), the victor through the companionship of the chief of the successors and through the company of his elder grandson (Imam Hasan). Peace be upon the one who was informed about the word by the chief of the truthful. May Allah curse your oppressive, wretched, accursed killer Hajjaj bin Yusuf Al-Saqafi. Peace be upon you, O Kumail bin Ziyaad al-Nakhai, al-Yamani. Divine mercy and blessings upon you.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAA AHADE HAWAA-RIYYA HABLIL-LAAHIL MATEE-NIL, FAA-E-ZE BE-SOHBATE SAYYADIL WASIYYEE-NA WA SOH-BATE SIBTE-HIL AKBARE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA MAN AKHBARA-HO BIL-QAWLE SAYYADIS SAADE-QEENA LA-A’NAL LAAHO QAATE-LA-KAZ ZAALE-MISH SHA-QIYYIL LA-EE’NIL HAJJAAJ-JIBNE YOOSU-FIS SAQA-FIYYE WAS SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA KUMAIY-LABNE ZIYAA-DIN NAKHA-I’YYIL YAMAANEE-YE WA RAHMA-TUL-LAAHE WA BARA-KAATO-HU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی اَحَدِ حَوَارِیَّ حَبْلِ اللهِ الْمَتِیْنِ، الْفَائِزِ بِصُحْبَۃِ سَیَّدِ الْوَصِیِّیْنَ وَ صُحْبَۃِ سِبْطِهِ الْاَكْبَرِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مَنْ اَخْبَرَهُ بِالْقَوْلِ سَیِّدِ الصَّادِقِیْنَ لَعَنَ اللهُ قَاتِلَكَ الظَّالِمِ الشَّقِیِّ اللَّعِیْنِ الْحَجَّاجِّ بْنِ یُوْسُفِ الثَّقَفِیِّ وَ السَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا كُمَیْلَ بْنِ زَیَادِ النَّخَعِیِّ الْیَمَانِیِّ وَ رَحْمَۃُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSig